name: R4-http-operations-for-R3
title: Cross-version VS for R4.TestScriptRequestMethodCode for use in FHIR R3
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/http-operations|4.0.1 for use in FHIR R3. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R4 to R3.
